      "id": "PopularPost99437",
      "post_content": "I prefer my poor man's Pyroclasm: [Tremor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tremor) + [Inflame](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Inflame)  \n  \nPros of Poor version  \n-Does more damage.  \n  \nCons of Poor version  \n-Doesn't hit players or creatures with flying  \n-Costs {R}{R} instead of {1}{R}  \n-Requires 2 cards instead of 1.",
      "posted_by": "Test-Subject_217601",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost99437\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">I prefer my poor man's Pyroclasm: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Tremor\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tremor\">Tremor</a> + <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Inflame\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Inflame\">Inflame</a><br/><br/>Pros of Poor version<br/>-Does more damage.<br/><br/>Cons of Poor version<br/>-Doesn't hit players or creatures with flying<br/>-Costs {R}{R} instead of {1}{R}<br/>-Requires 2 cards instead of 1.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '99437'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy40188\">Test-Subject_217601</span>\r\n                                (8/31/2010 9:02:18 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src