    {
      "id": "PopularPost222086",
      "post_content": "I *love* this card.  \n  \nI always play four of these in a mono-red burn deck, alongside four [Firespout](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Firespout). If I need a little more utility, I put one of each in the sideboard, to snag with a [Burning Wish](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Burning Wish). (Against noncreature decks that are low on critter removal, I sideboard in four [Magus of the Moon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Magus of the Moon).)  \n  \nThose two burn spells are massive card advantage in disguise, and critters not quite killed by the 'clasm can be targeted with a secondary burn spell. Not an ideal solution, but pretty good.",
      "posted_by": "Salient",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost222086\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">I <i>love</i> this card.<br/><br/>I always play four of these in a mono-red burn deck, alongside four <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Firespout\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Firespout\">Firespout</a>. If I need a little more utility, I put one of each in the sideboard, to snag with a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Burning Wish\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Burning Wish\">Burning Wish</a>. (Against noncreature decks that are low on critter removal, I sideboard in four <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Magus of the Moon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Magus of the Moon\">Magus of the Moon</a>.)<br/><br/>Those two burn spells are massive card advantage in disguise, and critters not quite killed by the 'clasm can be targeted with a secondary burn spell. Not an ideal solution, but pretty good.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '222086'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy67559\">Salient</span>\r\n                                (1/24/2012 7:40:13 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\